<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Call of Silence"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="澤野弘之"/><amll:meta key="album" value="「進撃の巨人」Season 2 原声带"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="222722273"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="Qim516"/></metadata></head><body dur="2:46.738"><div begin="38.206" end="2:46.738"><p begin="38.206" end="45.870" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="38.206" end="38.730">​Don&apos;t</span> <span begin="38.730" end="39.266">you</span> <span begin="39.266" end="40.654">think</span> <span begin="40.654" end="41.078">&apos;bout</span> <span begin="41.078" end="42.618">me</span> <span begin="42.618" end="45.286">enough?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你难道不够想我吗</span></p><p begin="45.870" end="53.644" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="45.870" end="46.463">I&apos;ve</span> <span begin="46.463" end="46.991">been</span> <span begin="46.991" end="48.486">burn</span><span begin="48.486" end="48.764">ing</span> <span begin="48.764" end="50.340">my</span> <span begin="50.340" end="50.812">heart</span> <span begin="50.812" end="52.699">out</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我内心备受煎熬</span></p><p begin="53.644" end="1:01.408" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="53.644" end="54.151">Got</span> <span begin="54.151" end="54.714">to</span> <span begin="54.714" end="55.917">face,</span> <span begin="56.100" end="56.376">need</span> <span begin="56.376" end="57.896">to</span> <span begin="57.896" end="58.392">tell</span> <span begin="58.392" end="1:00.396">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">必须面对面地告诉你</span></p><p begin="1:01.408" end="1:10.116" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:01.408" end="1:01.916">I</span> <span begin="1:01.916" end="1:02.288">won&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:02.288" end="1:04.576">run</span> <span begin="1:05.262" end="1:05.869">&apos;cause</span> <span begin="1:05.869" end="1:06.034">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:06.034" end="1:07.862">re</span><span begin="1:07.862" end="1:08.105">ti</span><span begin="1:08.105" end="1:10.116">cent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我虽然沉默寡言 但不会逃避</span></p><p begin="1:17.839" end="1:25.635" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:17.839" end="1:25.635">Oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哦</span></p><p begin="1:33.425" end="1:43.983" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:33.425" end="1:41.090">Ooh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哦</span></p><p begin="1:43.983" end="1:51.795" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:43.983" end="1:44.519">You</span> <span begin="1:44.519" end="1:44.981">will</span> <span begin="1:44.981" end="1:45.824">know</span> <span begin="1:45.824" end="1:46.461">you&apos;re</span> <span begin="1:46.461" end="1:46.917">re</span><span begin="1:46.917" end="1:47.795">born</span> <span begin="1:47.795" end="1:48.362">to</span><span begin="1:48.362" end="1:51.116">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你会知道今晚你将重生</span></p><p begin="1:51.795" end="1:59.490" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:51.795" end="1:52.222">Must</span> <span begin="1:52.222" end="1:52.695">be</span> <span begin="1:52.695" end="1:52.862">ra</span><span begin="1:52.862" end="1:53.045">gg</span><span begin="1:53.045" end="1:53.278">ed</span> <span begin="1:53.278" end="1:53.670">but</span> <span begin="1:53.670" end="1:54.062">I’ll</span> <span begin="1:54.062" end="1:54.719">stay</span> <span begin="1:54.719" end="1:55.674">by</span> <span begin="1:55.674" end="1:56.050">your</span> <span begin="1:56.050" end="1:58.614">side</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">必定很狼狈 但我始终在你身边</span></p><p begin="1:59.490" end="2:07.194" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:59.490" end="2:00.487">Even</span> <span begin="2:00.487" end="2:00.972">if</span> <span begin="2:00.972" end="2:01.444">my</span> <span begin="2:01.444" end="2:02.430">body&apos;s</span> <span begin="2:02.430" end="2:02.847">blea</span><span begin="2:02.847" end="2:03.139">ched</span> <span begin="2:03.139" end="2:03.406">to</span> <span begin="2:03.406" end="2:03.894">the</span> <span begin="2:03.894" end="2:06.571">bone</span><span begin="2:06.571" end="2:06.838">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">即使我的身躯消磨殆尽</span></p><p begin="2:07.194" end="2:14.441" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:07.194" end="2:07.725">I</span> <span begin="2:07.725" end="2:08.142">don’t</span> <span begin="2:08.142" end="2:08.704">want</span> <span begin="2:09.111" end="2:09.644">go</span> <span begin="2:09.644" end="2:10.094">through</span> <span begin="2:10.094" end="2:10.709">that</span> <span begin="2:10.709" end="2:11.525">ever</span> <span begin="2:11.525" end="2:14.021">again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我也不想再经历那种痛苦</span></p><p begin="2:14.441" end="2:18.378" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:14.441" end="2:14.951">So</span> <span begin="2:14.951" end="2:15.494">cry</span> <span begin="2:15.494" end="2:15.708">no</span> <span begin="2:15.708" end="2:17.558">more</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">所以别再哭泣</span></p><p begin="2:18.378" end="2:22.244" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:18.378" end="2:18.825">Oh</span> <span begin="2:18.825" end="2:19.314">my</span> <span begin="2:19.314" end="2:19.587">be</span><span begin="2:19.587" end="2:20.871">loved</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哦 我亲爱的</span></p><p begin="2:22.244" end="2:30.036" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:22.244" end="2:22.709">Go</span> <span begin="2:22.709" end="2:23.197">ahead,</span> <span begin="2:23.197" end="2:23.476">be</span> <span begin="2:23.476" end="2:24.868">proud</span> <span begin="2:25.213" end="2:25.360">and</span> <span begin="2:25.360" end="2:27.118">fight</span> <span begin="2:27.118" end="2:27.340">it</span> <span begin="2:27.340" end="2:29.071">out</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">放手去做 勇敢面对 奋力拼搏</span></p><p begin="2:30.036" end="2:33.887" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:30.036" end="2:30.521">You</span> <span begin="2:30.521" end="2:31.044">are</span> <span begin="2:31.044" end="2:31.280">the</span> <span begin="2:31.280" end="2:33.308">one</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你就是那个人</span></p><p begin="2:33.887" end="2:37.727" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:33.887" end="2:34.349">Our</span> <span begin="2:34.349" end="2:34.859">ris</span><span begin="2:34.859" end="2:35.111">ing</span> <span begin="2:35.111" end="2:36.833">star</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我们冉冉升起的新星</span></p><p begin="2:37.727" end="2:46.738" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:37.727" end="2:38.198">You</span> <span begin="2:38.198" end="2:38.765">guide</span> <span begin="2:38.765" end="2:39.068">us</span> <span begin="2:39.068" end="2:40.268">far</span> <span begin="2:40.689" end="2:40.968">to</span> <span begin="2:40.968" end="2:42.180">home</span> <span begin="2:42.595" end="2:42.955">yet</span> <span begin="2:42.955" end="2:46.738">girt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你指引我们从远方回到了家 依然坚守</span></p></div></body></tt>